# CODEOWNERS — auto-requests review from the listed owner(s) when matching
# paths change. See:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-customization/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# "Require approval from Code Owners" is NOT enabled in branch protection today
# (a solo maintainer cannot approve their own PR). The AI review
# (.github/workflows/review.yml) is the merge gate. This file documents intent
# + flags sensitive surfaces; enable Code Owner enforcement when a co-maintainer
# joins.

# Default owner — everything not matched below
